{"tid":374041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何詩蓓再摘金　200自決賽破大會紀錄封后","createTime":"2017-08-25T12:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T02:45:33.000Z","uid":62409,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a586d8b187bb7b206ef4b919fd9e9235d5b9d90e","tid":374041,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"於女子100米自由泳為奪金的何詩蓓，今晚再為香港增光。轉戰女子200米自由泳的她決賽游1分56.71秒，破世大運紀錄兼奪得今屆世大運個人第二面金牌。<br />\n<br />\n延續100米威勢，何詩蓓不惜放棄4x200米自由泳接力，而的確她於200米自由泳初賽、準決賽同樣列總成績第1名晉級。今晚的決賽她以大熱身份游出1分56.71秒摘下金牌，打破1分57.31秒舊紀錄。這是港隊今屆第2面獎牌，也是自韋漢娜2009年連奪兩金，加上歐鎧淳去屆的銀牌，香港歷來第5面世大游泳獎牌。賽事亞軍為美國的Katherine Grace Drabot，時間為1分57.61秒，俄羅斯的Arina Openysheva則奪得季軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/114545/thumbnail/bf9c61f4b410bef65f78d77192d46a56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F114545%2Fthumbnail%2Fbf9c61f4b410bef65f78d77192d46a56.jpg&h=a78b804b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ee3b1b5670c5dcdd007e7c299d2ecb482ca3e96","tid":374041,"uid":14021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138e499fd4d7dece1559f1d6f0de549a77a6ed9c","tid":374041,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f195f028419be3344933c013c396b93ff9f32d62","tid":374041,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fa1700bf7e52181096e4600049257fe487415f","tid":374041,"uid":12625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201